data.description: This 3 bedroom / 1 bath home offers 1,656 sq ft on 1.18 acres and BACKS NATIONAL FOREST ... large lot with lots of options.  This home has been updated in some respects and not in others so you really must see it.  There are some dual paned windows and some single paned windows.  A Diamond in the rough, if you will.  Plenty of room to park your RV, Travel Trailer, Boat, horse trailer etc...  Just had a new roof put on the home June 2023.
